description: This file defines the prototypes for custom data model processing functions related to NAT and Port Mapping in a network device, specifically for the Data Model implementation within the CCSP framework.

methods.name: NAT_GetParamBoolValue_Custom
methods.description: Retrieves the boolean value of a NAT parameter.

methods.name: NAT_SetParamBoolValue_Custom
methods.description: Sets the boolean value of a NAT parameter.

methods.name: PortMapping_GetParamUlongValue_Custom
methods.description: Retrieves the ULONG value of a port mapping parameter.

methods.name: PortMapping_SetParamUlongValue_Custom
methods.description: Sets the ULONG value of a port mapping parameter.
